0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=48a06abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"f3cc1a0df6d04696506954090a0f524932a939bc","tid":1771614,"uid":240885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"我 收成唔撚到 日日都不過是吊命"},{"pid":"22ab854a5dc5fbe93bd8d0a0d69cddc7f79599a0","tid":1771614,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29cb130b98cad458c9beccc481a1ea2feeac35f9","tid":1771614,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一撚樣 根本方方面都輸撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住塊鏡都想笑撚柒自己 咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己好短命<br />\n就算唔短命都好快死 唔會俾自己咁長命<br />\n係睇個時機姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18f3ea10819e65aa05522241bfbb846ffa0058b","tid":1771614,"uid":155846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ab854a5dc5fbe93bd8d0a0d69cddc7f79599a0","tid":1771614,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:15:43.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啦，就係付出完無回報先咁撚灰<br />\n我屌爆你老母個閪呀"},{"pid":"8f6a54c3fdc853f997e73b50085fe22493622ec3","tid":1771614,"uid":77833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f979d9d8a1300b2224f0f0597629e413c62e318","tid":1771614,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c88e544abe7a991ab70cf534f7f3225cea2ed09","tid":1771614,"uid":77833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:05:29.000Z","msg":"或許我不能完全了解你內心的痛苦，但我也曾置身於無助和絕望之中，明白身處痛苦是怎樣一回事。無論你的是否想放棄自己，也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=48a06abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7019dc3e4667c98a57ab8be92568fc3ffeb4e0","tid":1771614,"uid":95097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:27:34.000Z","msg":"老豆好後生就死左<br />\n唔鐘意講野 好輸蝕<br />\n好鐘意洗錢 成日洗突曬<br />\n同老婆得閒鬧交<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"9047ce0095dc4a6d7b139f8fb8a5e849e7a8e848","tid":1771614,"uid":32288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aceaa218ff3382cec97f9015530487ce7156e51","tid":1771614,"uid":165925,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T09:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"人生無常呀巴打 我相信苦盡會甘來<br />\n支持你 一定要撐住 唔好放棄呀！！！<br />\n更好嘅係後面等緊你<br />\n<br />\n利申 一個分手後有少少抑鬱從自殺中行返上嚟嘅人"},{"pid":"66dd3129b1bde195a9e6f77616d15e0568ef4080","tid":1771614,"uid":60813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f118e1f188cdbcd382dce17f5009dcca4d818c7f","tid":1771614,"uid":106050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"政府工好難先考到....<br />\n條仆街做左咩黎，正常唔係好難整走一個公務員嗎？"},{"pid":"04bbd37694b35a67140ad8663d5f26de585dea09","tid":1771614,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"我 但係我又冇話好唔開心 反而覺得已經養成左知足常樂 雖然陣間又可能比人話自己呃自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa5857e0e63d1333baaa9cd70d79cf9f08bcf182","tid":1771614,"uid":71197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"努力又是什麼<br />\n如果目標已經出錯"},{"pid":"30c8d002fc6450b9a04deca4dc00e0e087ba32af","tid":1771614,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"10歲打後唔開心居多<br />\n童年剩係識玩訓 所以冇咩事<br />\n到你要開始做決定 諗野既時候 冇咩野係easy /順利 通常都要你好撚努力 先猛車邊做到 甚至努力左都做唔到<br />\n出過外國 更明白有d野 係我地香港人天生 冇得改變 eg native language 膚色 你個姓名 文化<br />\n人地可以見到你個名係外國人名 自動filter 走個application <br />\n你見呢幾年韓日文化係鬼佬地區咁流行 而日韓人去到係會受尊重/注視 <br />\n幾時先輪到香港文化（懷念香港80年代果陣有文化輸出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n而家人地唔尊重你文化 亦都唔重視你既存在 簡單講即係佢don't give a fuc